snippet.title: Ex-Zodiac Trailer
snippet.description:
You can now wishlist the game on steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1249480/ExZodiac/

Yep, still chipping away at it! I've recently teamed up with Pixeljam Games who are going to help with the publishing and business side of things. Things should move a long a bit quicker now!
